1. Create Project
composer create-project laravel/laravel ecommerce --prefer-dist --version=10.*
2. .env file
	add db details

3. key generate
	php artisan key:generate

4. Admin Panel create / Ui
	composer require laravel/ui
	php artisan ui bootstrap --auth
	php artisan migrate
5. Alter table
	php artisan make:migration add_is_admin_to_users_table --table=users
6. Create Model & Migration
	php artisan make:model Logistics -m
7. Create controller with basic method
	php artisan make:controller LogisticsController --resource

 